OL,3,CWhat rests on today's US-Iran nuclear
OL,4,Ctalks
OL,6,FThe talks which get underway in Geneva
OL,7,Ftoday are the latest in negotiations
OL,8,Fbetween the US and Iran, they may well
OL,9,Fbe the last.
OL,11,FOfficially, what comes from the next
OL,12,Ffew hours will signal the direction of
OL,13,Ftravel for the Middle East and beyond.
OL,14,FIn reality that path may already be
OL,15,Fset, what happens today may simply the
OL,16,Fwindow dressing to justify what
OL,17,Ffollows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
