OL,3,CWhat rests on today's US-Iran nuclear
OL,4,Ctalks
OL,6,FThat could be managed tension and
OL,7,Fincremental diplomacy or escalation
OL,8,Fand military action. Donald Trump
OL,9,Fwarned the Iranians after the last
OL,10,Fround that "bad things" would happen
OL,11,Fif resolution could not be found.
OL,13,FThose "bad things" would have
OL,14,Fconsequences regionally and globally,
OL,15,Fon security and economies.
OL,17,FThey will have consequences on life
OL,18,Fand its survivability for those in the
OL,19,Fimmediate area and on life, its
OL,20,Fsecurity and cost for those beyond.
