OL,3,CWhat rests on today's US-Iran nuclear
OL,4,Ctalks
OL,6,FWhat's decided will determine how safe
OL,7,Fwe all are and how much we are
OL,8,Fspending on daily life.
OL,10,F"Bad things" would have massive
OL,11,Fconsequences, not least because it
OL,12,Fremains unclear what the military
OL,13,Fobjectives of action would be, what's
OL,14,Fto gain, how it would be executed and
OL,15,Ffor how long it could be sustained.
OL,17,F"Bad things" for Iran are potentially
OL,18,Fbad things for everyone.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@LO]yD@AOUyD@LO]
