OL,3,CWhat rests on today's US-Iran nuclear
OL,4,Ctalks
OL,6,FOn the face of it Washington is
OL,7,Fseeking to limit Iran's nuclear
OL,8,Fprogramme, to make it impossible for
OL,9,Fit to develop a nuclear weapon. Tehran
OL,10,Fwants sanctions relief and recognition
OL,11,Fof its right to a civilian nuclear
OL,12,Fprogramme.
OL,14,FHowever the US has alluded to taking
OL,15,Fout Iran's leadership, its missile
OL,16,Fstocks and proxies. Such mixed
OL,17,Fmessaging is bad for talks and bad for
OL,18,Faction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
