OL,3,CWhat rests on today's US-Iran nuclear
OL,4,Ctalks
OL,6,FPresident Trump may believe fast,
OL,7,Fisolated action such as he carried out
OL,8,Fin Venezuela offers a game plan for
OL,9,Fwhat comes next but history should not
OL,10,Fbe his guide.
OL,12,FThe dark history of US intervention in
OL,13,FIraq and Afghanistan offers a better
OL,14,Finsight as to what a misstep now could
OL,15,Funleash.
